OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening
OL,6,Fshowers, possibly thundery, slowly
OL,7,Fclearing eastwards. Cloudy with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain affecting parts of
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland and Scotland,
OL,10,Fotherwise dry with clear spells.
OL,11,FAnother warm night, especially in the
OL,12,Feast where itll be warmer than
OL,13,Fprevious nights.
OL,14,
OL,15,CFriday:FDry with sunny spells for
OL,16,Fmost, however outbreaks of rain will
OL,17,Faffect the far north, with showers
OL,18,Facross the southeast, where it will be
OL,19,Fanother very warm day. Cooler
OL,20,Felsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
